Author: losemore
Text: Count your blessings for your low alcohol tolerance as it’s a toxic trap to fall into. And I hope you find peace too, friend. ✨ Thank you for reading this poorly articulated ramble.

Author: Iamaloneanddepressed
Text: I hope shitposting gave you what you wanted it to. I hope you find peace. Binges are hard to get over. I dont know it I could drink a bottle of wine every night. I can barely manage two or three cocktails.
